---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<Layout
  title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`}
  description="About the Nomadic Year travel archive."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-none ny-preparation-page">
    <h1 class="sr-only">About Us</h1>

    <section class="ny-prep-hero">
      <p class="ny-prep-hero__kicker">About</p>
      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        We are Ivan and Hyein, originally from Russia and South Korea, living
        out of our Toyota Land Cruiser while driving around the world.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="ny-prep-section">
      <div class="ny-prep-card">
        <div class="ny-prep-card__media">
          <img
            class="ny-prep-card__image"
            src="/uploads/2016/04/about-us-photo-1024x683.jpg"
            srcset="/uploads/2016/04/about-us-photo-300x200.jpg 300w, /uploads/2016/04/about-us-photo-640x480.jpg 640w, /uploads/2016/04/about-us-photo-1024x683.jpg 1024w, /uploads/2016/04/about-us-photo.jpg 1500w"
            sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 900px"
            alt="Ivan and Hyein standing with their Land Cruiser"
            loading="eager"
            decoding="async"
            fetchpriority="high"
          />
        </div>

        <p>So i guess you want to know who we are.</p>
        <p>
          We are Ivan and Hyein, originally from Russia and South Korea, but
          live in California now.
        </p>
        <p>
          Live is an overstatement, since now we actually live in our lovely
          Toyota Land Cruiser 100 as we are on a quest to drive around the
          world.
        </p>
        <p>
          We started in San Diego, California and plan to drive through Central
          and South America. Afterwards we will ship the car to Korea, and
          while our home on wheels enjoys a cruise we will head to South East
          Asia to check out the sights as backpackers.
        </p>
        <p>
          Once we get the car in Korea, we will take a ferry to Vladivostok and
          drive west through Russia, Mongolia, the Stans and onto Europe.
        </p>
        <p>
          The plan was to do this in 1 year at about $100/day. Lets see if we
          can!
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
